<para>An edge is subdivided only if both its left and right triangles have aspect ratio below or equal to this value. So this is a maximum aspect ratio of a triangle that can be split on two before Delone optimization. Please set it to a smaller value only if frozenBoundary==true, otherwise many narrow triangles can appear near border </para>
        </detaileddescription>
